# The base agent needs no secrets: snapshot tools use a local JSON store.
#
# The similarweb and notion connections use Vercel Connect (app-scoped).
# Instead of pasting tokens here, run:
#   vercel link
#   vercel connect create similarweb
#   vercel connect create notion
#   vercel env pull
#
# Model access follows your eve setup (Vercel AI Gateway or a provider key).
